page.title: 14SHOPS WHICH SELL NEWSPAPERS
page.content: All these shops sell newspapers in Minehead:The Avenue Post Office,W.H.Smith,Newshop,N.S.S.Alcombe News.There are 12 daily,2 local weekly and 12 Sunday papers.Most of the papers are printed in London.The cheapest costs 18p and the dearest costs 40p.Newshop sells 600 each day.Some papers are delivered to people's homes.Boys and girls deliver the newspapers.The most popular paper is The Sun but The Daily Telegraph and Daily Mirror also sell well.The Guardian and The Star are the least popular.
